<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.10.10">
<l>vārārum mulaimaṭavāḷ vaitēvi taṉaikkaṇṭu</l>
<l>cīrārun tiṟalaṉumaṉ terinturaitta vaṭaiyāḷam</l>
<l>pārārumpu kaḻpputuvaip paṭṭarpirāṉ pāṭalvallār</l>
<l>ērārum vaikuntat timaiyavarō ṭiruppārē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master the song of the lord and scholar of Putuvai,</l>
<l rend="indent">with glory that fills the earth,</l>
<l>[about] the proof that was known and,</l>
<l rend="indent">by brave and virtuous Hanuman,</l>
<l>told to Vaidevī, the simple woman with bodiced breasts,</l>
<l rend="indent">when [he] saw her,</l>
<l>Will live with the celestials in beautiful Vaikuntha.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
